<html><head><title>Hunt</title></head> <body bgcolor="#000000" text="#FFFFFF" vlink = "#99cccc" link = "#99ccff"  topmargin=0leftmargin=0 ><TABLE border = "0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="5"><TR><TD valign = middle align = left  height = 300 ><font size="+1">And to a certain point I still am. I've been ordained as a Baptistminister. A fellow preacher was a Marine who went out at nights and collected VC ears.The bullshit from the religious groups left me sick. I'm not mad with God. I'm sick ofso called righteous people. But they seek something that only a war can let you<A HREF ="hunt6.html">see.</A></font><p>JJoel Hunt Sr.</TD></TR></table></body></html> 